Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:31.94,screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFZFW-ZHENZTJF-L\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(970,700)}我们的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.01,0:24:56.02,screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord1\fs100\fsp15\fnFZFW-ZHENZTJF-L\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,700)}寻求改变的少年
